{"id": 1811, "genre": 1001, "title": "说起来，你想给宜家提点啥意见？", "description": "无论你把它当餐厅、家具店还是家居指南。", "record_count": 3449, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170720115243orjvL4xZzEyPk2BU.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-07-24T03:00:49Z", "options": [{"id": 224513, "content": "开网店吧，每次都要自己运回家好累啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 90, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 410105}, {"id": 224514, "content": "请快来我们这开店！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 39, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 789122}, {"id": 224515, "content": "2017宜家指南p94第四行末尾少了一个字", "image": null, "praise_count": 105, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 131713}, {"id": 224517, "content": "控制内部容纳顾客数量。", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 129480}, {"id": 224518, "content": "黄色购物袋可售。谢谢??", "image": null, "praise_count": 64, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 49249}, {"id": 224519, "content": "质量高一点……", "image": null, "praise_count": 49, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1086467}, {"id": 224520, "content": "不再卖家具，只开餐馆并买食品", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 219476}, {"id": 224521, "content": "不再卖家具，只开餐馆并卖食品", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 219476}, {"id": 224522, "content": "质量再好点", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1259397}, {"id": 224523, "content": "浙江门店太少", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 770553}, {"id": 224524, "content": "我没去过宜家 谢谢", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 696369}, {"id": 224525, "content": "允许顾客躺床上不超过10分钟！", "image": null, "praise_count": 78, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 126152}, {"id": 224781, "content": "质量不好，价格还挺高", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 719707}, {"id": 224526, "content": "敢不敢把东西做的好吃点", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1079529}, {"id": 224782, "content": "宜家已经变成老年人夏天避暑胜地！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1088215}, {"id": 224527, "content": "柜子的质量敢再好一点吗？敢不敢不掉皮？", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1025182}, {"id": 224528, "content": "做好平台的假冒伪劣产品的防范，有多家平台可以合作，可以跟平台对打假进行深层次合作。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 671978}, {"id": 225808, "content": "没去过", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 211089}, {"id": 224530, "content": "柜子和书架的底板质量得翻倍才行啊，刨花板随时掉下来……", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1086512}, {"id": 224531, "content": "开网店吧！满减优惠加包邮！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1007288}, {"id": 224532, "content": "单独开个店卖千元内小物件", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 948462}, {"id": 224534, "content": "希望可以在餐厅里多一些位置   每次去吃饭都找不到座位?", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1086540}, {"id": 229142, "content": "能不能做些质量好价钱稍贵的产品？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1103601}, {"id": 224535, "content": "珠海没有宜家啊，珠海没有宜家啊，珠海没有宜家啊，。。。重要的事情说三遍????", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1035441}, {"id": 224539, "content": "能不能给个快速通道，着急买了回家还要提着东西走完全区真的太痛苦了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 888133}, {"id": 224541, "content": "广州宜家能不能多在地下多搞点停车场啊，买个东西还得来回走一公里的路停车！", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1086563}, {"id": 224542, "content": "能来新疆开店吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 207346}, {"id": 234782, "content": "每次都只能去就近城市买，小物件还好，上次买了儿童床，把7座的车塞满了，着实不容易", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1129868}, {"id": 224543, "content": "必须有快速离开通道！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 588164}, {"id": 224799, "content": "标签不要那么长，分辨宜家的东西可能靠标签", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 171264}, {"id": 224544, "content": "速度开网店，不要对抗时代趋势", "image": null, "praise_count": 36, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 842788}, {"id": 224545, "content": "成都宜家餐厅的冷串串不好吃！价格贵！还有就是能开网店配送就好了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 720398}, {"id": 224546, "content": "销售瑞典当地生产的“瑞典肉丸”。", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 884357}, {"id": 224802, "content": "强烈建议宜家恢复“卤肉饭”！卤肉饭！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1079061}, {"id": 224548, "content": "用心做美食，不要不务正业搞家居", "image": null, "praise_count": 100, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 78222}, {"id": 224550, "content": "像我这种选择障碍，需要走回头路啊喂", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1086599}, {"id": 224807, "content": "不买就让他走啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1088551}, {"id": 224554, "content": "把那些到处躺尸不动的人弄走", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 882331}, {"id": 224811, "content": "再远都可以有偿送货好么", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 852189}, {"id": 224556, "content": "降低运费+扩大送货范围", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 882331}, {"id": 224557, "content": "快速离开通道刚需", "image": null, "praise_count": 33, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 453639}, {"id": 227117, "content": "概念好，但平价的组装家俱通常只能“装”一次！质量真心有点差！", "image": "img/option/option/20170804044201KPJYw249AgRkizQx", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 75333}, {"id": 224558, "content": "多开点店，最好家门口就能逛", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1013245}, {"id": 227118, "content": "餐厅的菜色可以换换了！多久了呀？！??", "image": "img/option/option/20170804045012Pl2O7N1xiaKo5z6k", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 75333}, {"id": 224559, "content": "我要走一圈才能出去，真的很费时间", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1086474}, {"id": 224560, "content": "石家庄什么时候开", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1008714}, {"id": 224816, "content": "安装费可以低一点吗？不想自己安装！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1088600}, {"id": 224561, "content": "人也比较多", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1086474}, {"id": 224563, "content": "空调太低了", "image": "img/option/option/201707241448209bVG5NzWL86Ya3pl.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1086629}, {"id": 224565, "content": "你们的那个APP能不能做得可以被我们使用而不是闪退或者一直转圈直到天荒地老也没用的那种？App Store上面的评论能关注一下吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 92160}]}